Available Tools: list_commits | get_commit | create_branch | delete_branch | list_branches | compare_branches
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "owner": "string", "repo": "string", "branch": "string", "sha": "string" }
Response Schema: { "commits": [{ "sha": "string", "message": "string", "author": "string", "date": "string" }], "branch": "string" }
---
Question: Display all branches for the stark-industries/arc-reactor repository.
Call: { "func_call": "list_branches", "owner": "stark-industries", "repo": "arc-reactor", "branch": "", "sha": "" }
Response: { "commits": [], "branch": "main" }

Question: Generate a new hotfix branch named hotfix/energy-leak in the stark-industries/arc-reactor repo based on commit f00dface.
Call: { "func_call": "create_branch", "owner": "stark-industries", "repo": "arc-reactor", "branch": "hotfix/energy-leak", "sha": "f00dface" }
Response: { "commits": [], "branch": "hotfix/energy-leak" }

Question: Remove the outdated experiment branch experiment/jarvis-v1 from the stark-industries/arc-reactor project.
Call: { "func_call": "delete_branch", "owner": "stark-industries", "repo": "arc-reactor", "branch": "experiment/jarvis-v1", "sha": "" }
Response: { "commits": [], "branch": "experiment/jarvis-v1" }

